description:
Description: 
Magic Excel Recovery 2.6 Commercial + Office + Home Magic Excel Recovery is a program for recovering deleted Excel spreadsheet files. After a quick installation and startup, click the Next button, the Options button appears, click and choose Russian support. Further from us it is required to specify the letter of the hard disk which should be scanned for missing files. Select, specify the type of scan (fast or full, the second will take longer), after the process has received files, mark the necessary, restore. Everything is as simple as possible, in fact, as in other developments from these authors. 

Developer: East Imperial Soft 
License: ShareWare - for you for nothing 
Language: English + Russian version
